    "body": "<p><b>Original Confluence URL:</b> <a href=\"https://qbdocs.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IAM/pages/1076658859\">https://qbdocs.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IAM/pages/1076658859</a> - please cross-check the quality of the ZD article with the Confluence counterpart and remove this line before publishing the ZD article</p>\n\n<h2>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul class=\"toc\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#header-1\">Prerequisites:</a></li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#header-3\">Step 0: Login with the API Token User</a></li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#header-5\">Step 1: Navigate to API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#header-6\">Step 2: Navigate to Tokens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#header-7\">Step 3: Create Token</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#header-8\">Step 4: Store token</a></li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n</ul><p>See <ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"inline\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Naming conventions in Okta\" ri:version-at-save=\"9\"></ri:page><ac:link-body>Naming conventions in Okta</ac:link-body></ac:link> </p><hr><h1 id=\"header-1\">Prerequisites:</h1><p>Client have to use different API tokens.</p><p>All API tokens that are used by applications should be created with the API token user. This is a shared user that must only be used to create API Tokens. Tokens that are created must be stored in a shared secret store (like KeePass). They cannot be viewed in the Okta UI.</p><p></p><h2 id=\"header-3\">Step 0: Login with the A<ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"b3a05921-278a-4d00-9d51-08457e49e5ac\">PI Token User</ac:inline-comment-marker>\n</h2><h3 id=\"header-5\">Step 1: Navigate to API</h3><img src=\"https://discoverxi-supportdesk.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/20716432835346\" alt=\"Screenshot_2019-11-28 Questback - Dashboard.png\"><p></p><h3 id=\"header-6\">Step 2: Navigate to Tokens</h3><img src=\"https://discoverxi-supportdesk.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/20716428751250\" alt=\"Screenshot_2019-11-28 Questback - API.png\"><p></p><h3 id=\"header-7\">Step 3: Create Token</h3><p><strong>Values:</strong></p><p>Name: clientâ€™s name</p><img src=\"https://discoverxi-supportdesk.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/20716428636690\" alt=\"Screenshot_2019-11-28 Questback - API(1).png\"><p></p><h3 id=\"header-8\">Step 4: Store <ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"29d7a3cd-791e-4d5b-82c2-82c5bf553381\">token</ac:inline-comment-marker>\n</h3><img src=\"https://discoverxi-supportdesk.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/20716428551314\" alt=\"Screenshot_2019-11-28 Questback - API(2).png\"><p></p>",
